    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-10-05T17:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-10-05T17:00:00-05:00" n="331"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d331">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 652.119/66</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Spain</hi> (<persName corresp="frus1917Supp02v01#p_WJE1"
                        type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Willard</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-10-05T17:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 5, 1917, 5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>697. Your 797, September 21, 12 noon. At present cannot facilitate departure <hi
                        rend="italic">Bartolo</hi>, as United States needs coal and nitrates.</p>
                <p>Pending settlement of British-Spanish agreement regarding fuel and iron ore
                    cannot release oil and coal for Spain. Therefore cannot release <hi
                        rend="italic">Cataluña</hi>. Further, cannot release oil or gasoline unless
                    assured as to consignees.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="frus1917Supp02v01#p_LR1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
